description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Cooter purrs with a rating of 75, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 225, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Leverage for North, Nine Lives for East, Leverage for South, and 5 for West. Cooter has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/90753-69652-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Cooter [225 Votes, Top 5% Score]
